Detailed Description

A helper struct bundling an object identifier and version.

The struct either contains the object's identifier and version (if it is registered or mapped), EQ_ID_INVALID and VERSION_NONE if it is unmapped or EQ_ID_NONE and VERSION_NONE if no object was given.
